title: Start
body:
???: YooooooOooOOOOOOOO~!!!! *crash*
P: …
<<place right Becky>>
<<Enter Becky right>>
???: …
<<emote Becky flirty>>
<<FadeUp Becky>>
P: …..
<<FadeUp Becky>>
???: *stands and brushes self off* [Matter of factly] 
<<FadeUp Becky>>
Hey Protag, are you from Damascus?
<<FadeUp Becky>>
Because you’re looking as sharp as steel.
P: … Becky. 
Becky.curious: Yes?
P: … Nevermind.
Becky: You sure?
P: Anyways… how’d your late night rendezvous go?
Becky.default: Oh, we chatted for a little while. You know, tested the waters.
Becky: And we really hit it off, right? Like, we talked for a good 45 minutes. So then I-
P: So it didn’t work out.
Becky.offended: Eh!? I didn’t even say anyth-
P: You know what you did.
Becky.default: Geh.
P: So? What happened after that?
Becky: Turns out she really doesn’t like the idea of using a kazoo to-
P: You don’t say. 
:*DING DONG THE FUCKING BELL*
P: Oh wait! We’re meeting up with June and Sammy after school today, right? At that cat café?
Becky: Yup! I’ll meet ya after class, okay? See ya!
